<emphasis id="E41622AF163AC1B5F8BB0CEC5C5BAA11" bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="11">A</emphasis>
Leafy stem showing distorted leaves 
<emphasis id="4E9A9E2071CD789144A172CDF3A41723" bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="11">B</emphasis>
